place_results.title: Mountain Goat Adventures
place_results.address: Kasaridih - Borsi Rd, Chowk, Durg, Chhattisgarh 491001
place_results.open_state: Closes soon · 8 pm · Opens 9 am Wed

most_relevant.description: I wanted to go to kerela for my honeymoon. So, i searched about the trip on the internet. A day after that, i got 12 calls and 8 messages from different numbers to book my trip including kerala tourism. I contacted mountain goat adventures and got the cheapest deal for 8 days 7 nights including travelling fare. The owner himself is an experienced traveller and explorer. My experience with mountain goat adventures was really great. Looking forward to book more trips...
